For script, add comand line: sudo ln /home/odr/dab/config/supervisor/*.conf /etc/supervisor/conf.d/
and sudo ln /home/odr/dab/config/*.conf /etc/supervisor/conf.d/
For linking all the "config" directory in supervisor

after the git clone repository "RPIDAB_AIO" move the "config" file in root of "dab" directory
mv /home/$USER/dab/RPIDAB_AIO/config /home/$USER/dab/



in sudo nano /etc/supervisor/supervisord.conf

add 2 lines:

[include]
files = /etc/supervisor/conf.d/*.conf /etc/supervisor/conf.d/*/*.conf /etc/supervisor/conf.d/*/*/*.conf


